data.description: Back on the market - no fault of the seller!  New roof installed Sept 2023 and new neutral paint upstairs!  Much larger than it appears.  From the charming front porch to the beautiful back yard with vinyl liner pool, this two-story home offers multiple living spaces, designed for seamless family living and entertaining.  The main level includes the great room, separate dining area, eat-in kitchen and spacious owner’s suite. Upstairs are 2 bedrooms, bathroom and multipurpose bonus room.  A fully finished basement includes living area, kitchen, 2 bedrooms. full bathroom, outside entrance-suitable as extra living space or a great rental opportunity.  The outdoor space with a large deck and pool is sure to become a favorite gathering spot.  This unique lot is 1.43 acres and includes an RV pad (or boat storage) with a 50 amp electrical hookup and room for a playground or other recreation.  The Dacula location provides convenient access to local schools, shopping centers, Gwinnett County park and recreational facilities, and access to I-85 or Hwy 316.
